kind: Workflow
metadata:
  generateName: add-song-to-playlist-
spec:
  entrypoint: main
  templates:
  - name: main
    dag:
      tasks:
      - name: get-playlist-id
        template: get-playlist-id
      - name: add-song-to-playlist
        template: add-song-to-playlist
        arguments:
          parameters:
          - name: user_ID
            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.user_ID }}'
          - name: playlist_ID
            value: '{{ tasks.get-playlist-id.result }}'
          - name: song_name
            value: 'Dancing Queen'
  - name: get-playlist-id
    http:
      url: http://example.com/api/Playlistname2ID
      method: POST
      headers:
        Content-Type: application/json
      body: |
        {
          "playlist_name": "Latin Fiesta"
        }
  - name: add-song-to-playlist
    http:
      url: http://example.com/api/AddSongToPlaylist
      method: POST
      headers:
        Content-Type: application/json
      body: |
        {
          "user_ID": "{{ inputs.parameters.user_ID }}",
          "playlist_ID": "{{ tasks.get-playlist-id.result }}",
          "song_name": "Dancing Queen"
        }
  arguments:
    parameters:
    - name: user_ID
      value: 123

apiVersion: argoproj.io/v1alpha1
kind: Workflow
metadata:
  generateName: movie-ticket-booking-
spec:
  entrypoint: main
  templates:
  - name: main
    dag:
      tasks:
      - name: find-showtime
        template: find-showtime
      - name: book-movie-ticket
        template: book-movie-ticket
        arguments:
          parameters:
          - name: movie_name
            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.movie_name }}'
          - name: showtime
            value: '{{ tasks.find-showtime.outputs.parameters.showtime }}'
          - name: number_of_tickets
            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.number_of_tickets }}'
  - name: find-showtime
    http:
      url: "http://api.example.com/findshowtime"
      method: "GET"
      parameters:
      - name: movie_name
        value: '{{ inputs.parameters.movie_name }}'
      - name: location
        value: '{{ inputs.parameters.city }}'
      - name: date
        value: '{{ inputs.parameters.date }}'
  - name: book-movie-ticket
    http:
      url: "http://api.example.com/bookmovieticket"
      method: "POST"
      parameters:
      - name: movie_name
        value: '{{ inputs.parameters.movie_name }}'
      - name: showtime
        value: '{{ inputs.parameters.showtime }}'
      - name: number_of_tickets
        value: '{{ inputs.parameters.number_of_tickets }}'
  arguments:
    parameters:
    - name: movie_name
      value: "Drama Movie"
    - name: city
      value: "Seattle"
    - name: date
      value: "{{ inputs.parameters.date }}"
    - name: number_of_tickets
      value: "2"

apiVersion: argoproj.io/v1alpha1
kind: Workflow
metadata:
  generateName: purchase-book-
spec:

  templates:

      tasks:
      - name: buy-book

        arguments:
          parameters:
          - name: user_ID
            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.user_ID }}'
          - name: ISBN
            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.ISBN }}'
  - name: buy-book
    http:
      url: "http://example.com/api/buybook"
      method: POST
      headers:
        Content-Type: application/json
      body: |
        {
          "user_ID": "{{ inputs.parameters.user_ID }}",
          "ISBN": "{{ inputs.parameters.ISBN }}"
        }
    inputs:
      parameters:
      - name: user_ID
      - name: ISBN
    outputs:
      parameters:
      - name: purchase_status
        valueFrom:
          jsonPath: "$.purchase_status"
  arguments:
    parameters:
    - name: user_ID
      value: 'Jennifer'
    - name: ISBN
      value: '9780136042594'

apiVersion: argoproj.io/v1alpha1
kind: Workflow
metadata:
  generateName: enroll-course-
spec:
  entrypoint: main
  templates:
  - name: main
    dag:
      tasks:
      - name: get-student-id
        template: get-student-id
      - name: get-course-id
        template: get-course-id
      - name: enroll-course
        template: enroll-course
        arguments:
          parameters:
          - name: person_ID
            value: '{{ tasks.get-student-id.result }}'
          - name: subject_ID
            value: '{{ tasks.get-course-id.result }}'
          - name: semester
            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.semester }}'
  - name: get-student-id
    inputs:
      parameters:
      - name: student_name
        value: '{{ inputs.parameters.student_name }}'
    container:
      image: python:3.8
      command: [python]
      args: ['-c', "import requests; print(requests.get('http://api.example.com/studentname2id', params={'student_name': '{{ inputs.parameters.student_name }}'}).json()['student_ID'])"]
  - name: get-course-id
    inputs:
      parameters:
      - name: course_name
        value: '{{ inputs.parameters.course_name }}'
    container:
      image: python:3.8
      command: [python]
      args: ['-c', "import requests; print(requests.get('http://api.example.com/coursename2id', params={'course_name': '{{ inputs.parameters.course_name }}'}).json()['course_ID'])"]
  - name: enroll-course
    inputs:
      parameters:
      - name: person_ID
      - name: subject_ID
      - name: semester
    container:
      image: python:3.8
      command: [python]
      args: ['-c', "import requests; print(requests.post('http://api.example.com/enrollcourse', json={'person_ID': '{{ inputs.parameters.person_ID }}', 'subject_ID': '{{ inputs.parameters.subject_ID }}', 'semester': '{{ inputs.parameters.semester }}'}).json()['Enrollment confirmation'])"]
  arguments:
    parameters:
    - name: student_name
      value: 'johndoe@gmail.com'
    - name: course_name
      value: 'Microeconomics'
    - name: semester
      value: 'Fall'

apiVersion: argoproj.io/v1alpha1
kind: Workflow
metadata:
  generateName: enroll-course-
spec:
  entrypoint: main
  templates:
  - name: main
    dag:
      tasks:
      - name: get-student-id
        template: student-id
      - name: get-course-id
        template: course-id
      - name: enroll-course
        template: enroll
        arguments:
          parameters:
          - name: person_ID
            value: '{{ tasks.get-student-id.result }}'
          - name: subject_ID
            value: '{{ tasks.get-course-id.result }}'
          - name: semester
            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.semester }}'
  - name: student-id
    inputs:
      parameters:
      - name: student_email
        value: '{{ inputs.parameters.student_email }}'
    http:
      url: http://example.com/api/studentname2id
      method: POST
      headers:
        Content-Type: application/json
      body: |
        {
          "student_name": "{{ inputs.parameters.student_email }}"
        }
  - name: course-id
    inputs:
      parameters:
      - name: course_name
        value: '{{ inputs.parameters.course_name }}'
    http:
      url: http://example.com/api/coursename2id
      method: POST
      headers:
        Content-Type: application/json
      body: |
        {
          "course_name": "{{ inputs.parameters.course_name }}"
        }
  - name: enroll
    inputs:
      parameters:
      - name: person_ID
      - name: subject_ID
      - name: semester
    http:
      url: http://example.com/api/enrollcourse
      method: POST
      headers:
        Content-Type: application/json
      body: |
        {
          "person_ID": "{{ inputs.parameters.person_ID }}",
          "subject_ID": "{{ inputs.parameters.subject_ID }}",
          "semester": "{{ inputs.parameters.semester }}"
        }
  arguments:
    parameters:
    - name: student_email
      value: 'tony.stark@avengers.com'
    - name: course_name
      value: 'Programming'
    - name: semester
      value: 'Winter'

apiVersion: argoproj.io/v1alpha1
kind: Workflow
metadata:
  generateName: concert-ticket-booking-
spec:
  entrypoint: main
  templates:
  - name: main
    dag:
      tasks:
      - name: get-concerts
        template: get-concerts
      - name: book-ticket
        template: book-ticket
        dependencies: [get-concerts]

  - name: get-concerts
    http:
      url: "http://example.com/api/MusicConcert"
      method: "GET"
      headers:
        - name: "Content-Type"
          value: "application/json"
      queryParams:
        - name: venue
          value: "San Francisco"

  - name: book-ticket
    http:
      url: "http://example.com/api/BookEventTicket"
      method: "POST"
      headers:
        - name: "Content-Type"
          value: "application/json"
      body:
        event_ID: '{{ tasks.get-concerts.result }}'
        venue_ID: '{{ inputs.parameters.venue_ID }}'
        date: '{{ inputs.parameters.date }}'
  
  arguments:
    parameters:
    - name: venue_ID
      value: '123'  # Example value, replace with actual venue ID
    - name: date
      value: '2023-09-15'

apiVersion: argoproj.io/v1alpha1
kind: Workflow
metadata:
  generateName: book-film-festival-ticket-
spec:
  entrypoint: main
  templates:
  - name: main
    dag:
      tasks:
      - name: get-theater
        template: get-theater
      - name: get-showtime
        template: get-showtime
        dependencies: [get-theater]
      - name: book-ticket
        template: book-ticket
        dependencies: [get-showtime]
  - name: get-theater
    http:
      url: "http://api.example.com/GetMovieTheaters"
      method: "GET"
      headers:
        - name: city
          value: "Los Angeles"
  - name: get-showtime
    http:
      url: "http://api.example.com/MovieShowtimes"
      method: "GET"
      headers:
        - name: movie_name
          value: "Film Festival"
        - name: city
          value: "Los Angeles"
  - name: book-ticket
    http:
      url: "http://api.example.com/BookEventTicket"
      method: "POST"
      headers:
        - name: event_ID
          value: '{{ inputs.parameters.event_ID }}'
        - name: venue_ID
          value: '{{ tasks.get-theater.result }}'
        - name: date
          value: '2023-10-22'
